title: Cheryl Burke/ Alzheimer's
description: Priyanka leaves clown school after too much clowning around. Sean pokes fun at his acupuncture treatments. Cheryl Burke cha-chas onto the podcast to discuss Dancing with the Stars and her mom's Alzheimer's diagnosis.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
